Cell["\<\
if z < minSn, then there are no intersections. For example, when SS = 10, \
minSn is 0.948683 (snn will never be lower than 0.95 sn). Horizontal gray \
line has no intersections with thick curve for S(x)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9726790124945793`*^9, 
  3.9726792114391127`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"23bb1b02-d0e1-423a-858c-\
